<div class="container">
  <h1> Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
  <p>Here are some common questions about the Online Learning Platform:</p>

  <div class="card">
    <h3 class="faq-question">How do I enroll in a course?</h3>
    <p class="faq-answer">Currently, this site provides course information only. Contact the instructor or your course administrator to enroll.</p>
    </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h3 class="faq-question">Are the live sessions recorded?</h3>
    <p class="faq-answer">This depends on the instructor. Check the course description or event schedule for details.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h3 class="faq-question">Can I contact instructors directly?</h3>
    <p class="faq-answer">Yes, instructor contact details are listed on the <a href="/instructors">Instructors</a> page.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h3 class="faq-question">Do I need to log in to access content?</h3>
    <p class="faq-answer">No login is required. The site is open for browsing course and event information.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h3 class="faq-question">Can I cancel an event registration?</h3>
    <p class="faq-answer">This demo platform does not support registration or cancellation. Please contact an instructor directly.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h3 class="faq-question">Is this platform mobile-friendly?</h3>
    <p class="faq-answer">Yes. All pages use responsive CSS and can be accessed from phones or tablets.</p>
  </div>

</div>

